Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:09.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, she's being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the bullies are so awfully clichéd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:14.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:17.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear about the human experiments you're helping with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:22.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where I was headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:23.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me your excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you be the "raw material"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:30.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's fine to not have a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:59.26,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,You always lose the important things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.35,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the umbrella you just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.22,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still have a ton of that vinyl crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:07.43,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't care if it's an umbrella, but when you put your winning lottery ticket down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:10.40,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,and can't find it afterwards, that sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.90,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you always find other things when you're looking for something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:17.96,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we just think that the things we lose are really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.11,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,Evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.45,Drrr Chats,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.81,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:32.73,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,that my head might be awake while my body's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.11,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since my memories became hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,the time passing by has felt ambiguous as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long it's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:49.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've seen myself as a whole, even in my dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.41,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:59.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I see on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.28,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.61,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-repeating dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm trying to decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the dream never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, you said you didn't have to work today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:08.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After some calculations, I've found out that it's your first day off in 265 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face doesn't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:20.23,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He reads my mood on the face I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that people dream because their brains are sorting their memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that sudden question?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know why people dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:37.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, it's still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:40.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still many hurdles that medical science has yet to cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in neuroscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The term "REM" comes to mind when talking about dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:49.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You often dream during rapid eye movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.21,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:51.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, an underground doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.69,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what he really does though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:05:03.19,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to him that I can both continue my job as a transporter and have a place to stay. {well he is letting her stay here}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first we have to answer the question, "What are memories?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:16.28,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And lately, when we're together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:20.40,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've realized that I'm in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:28.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you think your memories are in your head, but we don't know that for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely there. Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go out somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the day off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm turning my cellphone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll unplug the network cable as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I won't even check my mailbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the whole day to ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ride on your horse to the vast sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps a trip to the spa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:05.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we're taking the day off, and as thanks for taking care of me, I'd like to cook for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Home cooking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for a recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so moved, Selty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:28.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me borrow this, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real life saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid me overslept this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured the fatigue of coming all the way to Tokyo was catching up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you could call this a "hunter's chance"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sit shoulder-to-shoulder with your pretty neighbor and look at the same book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:46.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No necktie? Or did you forget that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you didn't forget your wallet too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:10.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Russian Sus—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Yumacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Karisawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wasn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:24.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dengeki Bunko's Accel World came out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We bought it together, had some tea, and then headed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:34.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the maid in the café told me that he forgot his cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't ask customers then. {In notes. -des}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "I'm looking for Yumacchi—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost things? {the sign says the same}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write what you're looking for on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to walk around the city with that all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking everyone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cellphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:17.26,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I searching for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.01,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's cool now that Kaztano is safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:24.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I promised not to dig deeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.81,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri Pharmaceuticals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.29,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that they're working behind-the-scenes with the Awakusu Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:35.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and that they're connected to the North American Nebula Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:41.07,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm not going to learn anything by standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Karisawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some Russian sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Selty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a kitchen knife, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way too yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delectable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This extremely sweet burdoc,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bitterness of the miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Your cooking is just divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand. I got the taste wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Don't force yourself to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, honestly, you're a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:38.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you don't have watermelon cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:44.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about your sense of taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:48.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brain can't understand tastes that aren't in your DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since you don't need to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't seem to be an issue with the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play a game, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like I'm a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:05.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That annoys me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not treating you like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:11.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you've taught me many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:16.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have memories that stretch back 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my head has even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need memories from 100 years in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I always say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:29.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:37.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm forgetting my own face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:41.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't contact you during an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sonohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:26.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you lose this time, Mikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her shoes are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are so spiteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:38.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a pretty good idea who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:51.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida-kun was a bit scarier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, he just ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:16.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I often lost things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:20.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to cry and shout, "It's not here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:23.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my mom would always help me find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you have a kind mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my dad is too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:42.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me look, Ryuugamine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Kida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, she went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, catch you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:14.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.88,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vacant lots are pretty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:41.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's gone, you just forget what was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something here not too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something really big...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.70,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I get irritated when Shinra tells me to stop looking for my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:03.04,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But having a job and friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Do those make me feel human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:11.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, didn't you want to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:22.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there a tall, thin, blue building here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that old one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an old woman selling cigarettes on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good catch, transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:37.74,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel my head in this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for beautiful Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:02.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me what you're desperately looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:08.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked for many things today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to find some of them, but not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.78,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Since his bag was gone, I assumed he was at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.58,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:06.87,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,something felt different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a lot of bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put him back together with help from a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some harsh staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was blabbering some nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently his girlfriend was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she could only remember this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to know what we did to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:42.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that isn't nonsense; it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:51.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that he won't remember anything about us when he wakes up, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:56.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't erase memories that conveniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'll remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:05.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe to his home, maybe somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:14.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc, the chief and I put our trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:18.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still keeping our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:25.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you're living with a rather eccentric person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.04,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,about my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:36.59,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and the memories of several hundred years as a Dullahan in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.31,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:42.85,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, won't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask for seats for two people, the restaurant won't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating alone is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this mysterious, avant-garde dish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:29.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaage sushi, cheese sushi, mabo sushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prosciutto sushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:33.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is our sour cream sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to make sushi out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great service!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we got fortune cookies for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a fortune inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:08.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means you'll find what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you'd be that happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, Shinra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does yours say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine didn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.92,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:53.21,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my head cries when I'm sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:06.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.91,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.38,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'm smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:46.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your past or future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:48.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the eternity now. {In notes. -des}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:19.08,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, after a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:22.27,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream where I was whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:43.27,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:45.78,Drrr Hardsubs,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:17.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My love is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:20.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from the love where the more you seek for it, the more you get spoiled. {In notes. -des}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:22.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something more complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:25.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Love and Care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.80,0:24:28.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am what Seiji needs.
